      "observed_level": "BLQ",
      "frequency_of_testing": "Once",
      "listed_in_coa": "Yes/No",
      "comments": ""
    }}
  ]
}}

Rules:
- concentration_value: numeric. If "BLQ", use the LOQ value (typically 0.05). If "NA" or blank, use 0.
- symbol: use standard element symbol (Pb, As, Cd, Hg, Co, V, Ni, etc.)

